### Interactive Charging Station Map & Real-time Features Test

### 1. Get Interactive Stations with Filters
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/stations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "",
  "address": "",
  "latitude": 10.762622,
  "longitude": 106.660172,
  "maxDistanceKm": 20,
  "connectorTypes": ["CCS", "CHAdeMO"],
  "minPowerOutput": 50,
  "maxPricePerKwh": 5.0,
  "isAvailable": true,
  "status": "Active"
}

### 2. Get Nearby Stations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/nearby?latitude=10.762622&longitude=106.660172&radiusKm=15&connectorTypes=CCS,CHAdeMO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get Station Real-time Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/station/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Filter Stations by Connector Type (CCS)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/filter/connector/CCS?latitude=10.762622&longitude=106.660172&maxDistanceKm=25
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Stations with Time-based Pricing
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/pricing?latitude=10.762622&longitude=106.660172&showPeakHours=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get Real-time Charging Session Data
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/session/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Update Session with Current SOC and Power
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/session/1/update
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "currentSOC": 75,
  "currentPower": 45.5
}

### 8. Get Estimated Remaining Time
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/session/1/remaining-time?currentSOC=75&targetSOC=90
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Get Active Sessions for Driver
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/driver/1/active-sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Check Charging Completion
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/session/1/check-completion
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Get Current SOC Percentage
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/session/1/soc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Send Charging Completion Notification
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/RealTimeCharging/session/1/send-notification
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. Filter by CHAdeMO Connector (using nearby endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/nearby?latitude=10.762622&longitude=106.660172&radiusKm=30&connectorTypes=CHAdeMO
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 13. Filter by AC Connector (using nearby endpoint)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/nearby?latitude=10.762622&longitude=106.660172&radiusKm=20&connectorTypes=AC
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 14. Get Stations with Off-peak Pricing
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/pricing?latitude=10.762622&longitude=106.660172&showPeakHours=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 15. Search Stations with Advanced Filters
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/InteractiveMap/stations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

